                                                                             tensorflow.StringVector containers)
        \brief Resets resource containers associated with a target. containers is a vector of string representation of resource container names. When a resource container is reset, the resources held by the container will be released. In particular, all Variables in the container will become undefined. If Reset succeeds, this function will return OK(). Otherwise, this function will return an error status.
